9 gold medal events headlined by the final full day of track & field competition, the U.S. Women's National Team facing Brazil in the women's soccer final (live at 11 a.m.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.5359065882964017, \"rank\": 0.7789305803988842, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET) and Team USA men's basketball taking on host-nation France in the gold medal game (3:30 p.m.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999162714496032, \"rank\": 8.229591997054866e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9991007633183125, \"rank\": 0.0008239903281031828, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET).\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The co-hosts ofGold Zoneweighed in the last two fast-paced weeks:  Scott Hanson: \\\"I am so thankful NBC Sports allowed me to bring my 'RedZone energy' to the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1183, \"end\": 1195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scott Hanson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7593822344039132, \"rank\": 0.3155752012328616, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fifteen straight days of unscripted TV was one of the greatest challenges of my career, but I am thrilled that our audience has judgedGold Zoneto be a resounding success!\\\"\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrew Siciliano: \\\"Every member of our behind-the-scenes crew deserves a gold medal for their amazing work the last two weeks.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Siciliano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ten hours a day for 15 straight days?\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unreal.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saturday is going to be the best day yet.\\\"\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Matt Iseman: \\\"This is the third Olympics I have covered, but I have never experienced one like this.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Iseman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Iseman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Iseman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Iseman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like we had a front row seat to all the greatest moments in every last sport.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think theGold Zoneis the way the Olympics were always meant to be experienced, we just needed the technology to catch up!\\\"\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jac Collinsworth: \\\"We spent the last two weeks looking for moments that people would feel at home.Gold Zoneis a show with no rules and the most fun viewing experience you can possibly have.\\\"\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 2006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jac_Collinsworth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jac Collinsworth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jac_Collinsworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jac_Collinsworth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold Zonehas been a fan favorite throughout NBCUniversal's coverage of the 2024 Paris Olympics, guiding viewers through the best and most compelling Olympic moments from 7 a.m. - 5 p.m.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999991775115377, \"rank\": 8.224478505255606e-07, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET each day.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With up to 40 events happening simultaneously during the Paris Olympics,Gold Zonepresents viewers with can not-miss action and moments, offering the most comprehensive and all-encompassing live whip-around coverage of any Olympic Games to date.\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock is the streaming home of the 2024 Paris Olympics, providing fans with the most comprehensive Olympic destination in U.S. media history.\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a Summer Games first for Peacock, streams every sport and event, including all 329 medal events, and features full-event replays; all NBC programming; curated video clips; virtual channels; exclusive original programming; and more.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2908, \"end\": 2911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9838049789441194, \"rank\": 0.01646157341841388, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition toGold Zone,Peacock's original 2024 Paris Olympics programmingincludesOlympic Highlights with Kevin Hart & Kenan Thompson,Watch with Alex Cooper,andYour Daily Olympic Recap on Peacock.\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3030, \"end\": 3037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999998269972971, \"rank\": 1.727220010641151e-07, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 3125, \"end\": 3139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenan_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenan Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenan_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenan_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"score\": 0.8607573575018954, \"rank\": 0.16176470588237404, \"text\": \"Alex Cooper\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"